com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.net
Interface NetRoot

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
NetRootImpl
public interface NetRoot
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Root'.

The following features are supported:

  • Mixed
  • XMLNS Prefix Map
  • XSI Schema Location
  • Capability Ip Interface
  • Capability L2 Interface
  • Unit Ip Interface Unit
  • Unit L2 Interface Unit

See Also:
NetPackage.getNetRoot()
